'''婚飞'''某些[[昆虫|昆虫]][[交配|交配]]时的群集飞行行为，常见于[[蚂蚁|蚂蚁]]、[[白蚁|白蚁]]、[[蜜蜂|蜜蜂]]。此外，[[蜉蝣|蜉蝣]]、[[石蛾|石蛾]]、[[石蝇|石蝇]]以及许多较为低等的[[双翅目|双翅目]]昆虫都具有婚飞的群体繁殖行为。<ref name="Hart 2018">{{cite journal |doi=10.1111/ecog.03140 |title=The spatial distribution and environmental triggers of ant mating flights: using citizen-science data to reveal national patterns |journal=Ecography |volume=41 |issue=6 |pages=877–888 |year=2018 |last1=Hart |first1=Adam G. |last2=Hesselberg |first2=Thomas G. |last3=Nesbit |first3=Rebecca |last4=Goodenough |first4=Anne E. |url=http://eprints.glos.ac.uk/4780/1/Hart%20et%20al%20flying%20ants.pdf |access-date=2020-12-10 |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430201016/http://eprints.glos.ac.uk/4780/1/Hart%20et%20al%20flying%20ants.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-40632535|title=Viewpoint: Is there such a thing as 'flying ant day'?|last=Hart|first=Adam|date=18 July 2017|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|language=en|access-date=17 July 2019|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310115928/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-40632535|dead-url=no}}</ref>
==白蚁==
有翅型 （alate）[[白蚁|白蚁]]会在一年中的某些特定时间出现进行婚飞。他们会倾巢而出，靠飛行進行長距離移動，交配後建立新群體，成為創始蟻王[[蟻后|蟻后]]<ref name="techreport">{{cite techreport|first1=M.A.|last1=Horwood|first2=R.H.|last2=Eldridge|title=Termites in New South Wales Part 1. Termite biology|number=96-38|institution=Forest Resources Research|year=2005|url=http://www.dpi.nsw.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0016/252007/Termites-Part-1--Termite-biology.pdf|issn=0155-7548|access-date=2020-12-10|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227214345/http://www.dpi.nsw.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0016/252007/Termites-Part-1--Termite-biology.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蟻后負責產卵，蟻王負責讓卵受精<ref name="Keller1998">{{cite journal|title=Queen lifespan and colony characteristics in ants and termites|first1=L.|journal=Insectes Sociaux|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s000400050084|year=1998|volume=45|pages=235–246|last1=Keller}}</ref>。
==蚂蚁==
[[Image:Meat_eater_ant_nest_swarming.jpg|right]]
有翅[[螞蟻|螞蟻]]會爬出蟻窩並且在空中進行婚飛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://antnest.co.uk/colony.html|title=How does an ant colony start?|accessdate=2008-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811140333/http://antnest.co.uk/colony.html|archive-date=2011-08-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同種螞蟻會選在同一時刻進行婚飛，雌蟻會飛行大段距離，和多隻雄蟻進行交配。交配过程中，雄蟻會將[[精子|精子]]放入至雌蟻的受精囊中。在交配過後，雄蟻即死去，而雌蟻會去尋找適合製作蟻窩的地點，一旦找到地點後，雌蟻的翅膀就會脫落。<ref name="Ant mating">{{cite web|title=Preparation for the mating flight|url=http://ant.edb.miyakyo-u.ac.jp/INTRODUCTION/Gakken79E/Page_25.html|accessdate=2007-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717231344/http://ant.edb.miyakyo-u.ac.jp/INTRODUCTION/Gakken79E/Page_25.html|archive-date=2011-07-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==蜜蜂==
[[蜂后|蜂后]]出房后五六天会远离母巢来到一个雄蜂聚集地进行交配飞行，它会与数只雄蜂进行交配然后返回。雄蜂则在交配之后死去。<ref name="Tautz">Jürgen Tautz: ''Phänomen Honigbiene.'' Mit Fotografien von Helga R. Heilmann. Elsevier, Spektrum Akademischer Verlag, München 2007, ISBN 978-3-827418-45-6.</ref>
==蜉蝣==
春夏两季，从午后至傍晚，成群的[[蜉蝣|蜉蝣]]雄虫会进行“婚飞”，雌虫独自飞入群中与雄虫配对。<ref name=Spieth>{{cite journal |author=Spieth, Herman T. |year=1940 |title=Studies on the biology of the Ephemeroptera. II. The nuptial flight |journal=Journal of the New York Entomological Society |volume=48 |issue=4 |pages=379–390 |jstor=25004879 }}</ref>
==双翅目==
婚飞在[[双翅目|双翅目]]的多个类群中普遍存在，如[[长角亚目|长角亚目]]的[[蚊|蚊]]、[[蚋|蚋]]、[[蠓|蠓]]，及[[短角亚目|短角亚目]]的[[虻|虻]]、[[蝇|蝇]]等。在婚飞中进行交配，促成远缘繁殖。<ref name=scm>{{cite journal |author1=王孟卿 |author2=杨定 |coauthors=陈红印 |title=双翅目昆虫的婚飞 |journal=昆虫知识 |date=2010 |issue=6 |pages=1280-1286|url=http://www.ent-bull.com.cn/admin/downfile.aspx?id=14038}}</ref>
